Interface MatchResult

All Known Subinterfaces:
MutableMatchResult, SchedulableMatchResult
All Known Implementing Classes:
MutableMatchResultImpl, SchedulableMatchResultImpl
public interface MatchResult

This interface models an entity which will contain all assignments made during matching phase.
